      "text": "both the operating system and the CPU architecture that are fixed Nothing is left for a VM to decide",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "both the operating system and the CPU architecture that are fixed Nothing is left for a VM to decide",
